{"tid":1631386,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請謹記及互相提醒動武應符合比例原則","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:23:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T15:28:10.000Z","uid":213898,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d1d3e4c026501065d42211e177907801eb000f35","tid":1631386,"uid":213898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:23:13.000Z","msg":"明白前線經過咁多不公義怒氣沖天<br />\n絕對理解，每個香港人都好嬲<br />\n希望大家以大局為重，唔好貪一時之氣主動出手<br />\n影大頭及口角未至於動武<br />\n除非對方持致命武器，例如利器，踩油<br />\n否則手足手痕都要忍（引）到出方出手<br />\n先<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">出鶳有名</span></span><br />\n現實係香港一定要獲國際支持，文宣極重要<br />\n希望前線，fa，街坊互相禮貌提醒<br />\n做到真以武制暴<br />\n<br />\n敬祝武運亨通"},{"pid":"c6a92545e17c3391420222bd57201c55247aa0d1","tid":1631386,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:24:15.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"fe11dfea48e6d333df6e94f72b99b37cec6c400b","tid":1631386,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:24:20.000Z","msg":"黑紅藍黃<br />\n鶳都要合乎比例啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【地方的手足需要進化】麻煩大家入黎溫下書，睇下烏克蘭係E個時候做左D咩<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631278\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631278</a>"},{"pid":"a13ecc455856d837b29e9e29dfe33ca32cdd1193","tid":1631386,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:25:05.000Z","msg":"極端勇武同埋極端左膠都唔係好事"},{"pid":"bc5b3a6d68fc725b10ec44135c33701decf3568a","tid":1631386,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:25:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EGMpntHXoAIZCXK?format=jpg&amp;name=900x900\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEGMpntHXoAIZCXK%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3D900x900&h=ba0d8cd3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"04dd3c246dcac22ecaed17eaaf9b9ebd85a3aaa7","tid":1631386,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:28:10.000Z","msg":"知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">「極重要」《三份英國外交及國會報告》：當代及後世香港抗爭者之啟示</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631132\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631132</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}